    "text": "Ooh, I don't think so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.9,
    "endTime": 21.33,
    "text": "No, anecdotal evidence suggests that in a game of rock, paper, scissors,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.33,
    "endTime": 27.299999999999997,
    "text": "players familiar with each other will tie 75% to 80% of the time due to the limited number of outcomes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.3,
    "endTime": 30.947,
    "text": "I suggest rock, paper, scissors, lizard, Spock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.71,
    "endTime": 33.543,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.543,
    "endTime": 35.33,
