  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.43,
    "endTime": 84.7,
    "text": "What do you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.9,
    "endTime": 88.65,
    "text": "I need access to the Cheesecake Factory's walk-in freezer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.65,
    "endTime": 108.80000000000001,
    "text": "Yeah, honey, I already told you, the hamburger meat is fresh and stored at a safe temperature."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.97,
    "endTime": 110.343,
    "text": "Oh, dear God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.24,
    "endTime": 115.05999999999999,
    "text": "Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.06,
    "endTime": 116.49300000000001,
    "text": "Leonard, I'm sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.4,
    "endTime": 123.68100000000001,
    "text": "Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.4,
    "endTime": 125.18100000000001,
    "text": "Leonard, I'm sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.9,
    "endTime": 130.324,
    "text": "Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.8,
    "endTime": 132.87900000000002,
    "text": "Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.34,
    "endTime": 135.173,
    "text": "Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 142.325,
    "text": "Leonard, my comforter fell down and my sinuses hurt when I bend over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.85,
    "endTime": 158.471,
    "text": "My Incredible Hulk hands signed by Stan Lee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.16,
    "endTime": 162.727,
    "text": "Oh, my."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.95,
    "endTime": 183.01999999999998,
    "text": "I've admired these for years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.02,
    "endTime": 185.69,
    "text": "Does that mean we can go with the girls again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.69,
    "endTime": 188.613,
    "text": "Hulk agrees to second date with puny humans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.59,
    "endTime": 192.4,
    "text": "Hey Shelley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.8,
    "endTime": 194.9,
    "text": "What ya doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.9,
    "endTime": 196.6,
    "text": "Size ratio was all wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.6,
    "endTime": 199.459,
    "text": "Couldn't visualize it. Needed bigger carbon atoms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.8,
    "endTime": 202.17200000000003,
    "text": "Sure, sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.09,
    "endTime": 206.32,
    "text": "How did you get into this place?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.32,
    "endTime": 212.2,
    "text": "The back door has a five pin tumbler system, single circuit alarm, child's play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.31,
    "endTime": 216.653,
    "text": "You can start sorting protons and neutrons while I build carbon atoms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.52,
    "endTime": 218.58,
    "text": "No, I don't think so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.58,
    "endTime": 220.173,
    "text": "We need to go home now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.13,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "But I'm still working."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
    "endTime": 226.8,
    "text": "If you don't come out of there, I'm gonna have to drag you out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.94,
    "endTime": 230.59,
    "text": "You can try, but you'll never catch me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.8,
    "endTime": 235.43200000000002,
    "text": "For God's sake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.9,
    "endTime": 243.4,
    "text": "Sheldon, come here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.5,
    "endTime": 244.1,
    "text": "Bazinga."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.1,
    "endTime": 248.214,
    "text": "Bazinga."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.4,
    "endTime": 251.489,
    "text": "Bazinga."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.37,
    "endTime": 254.203,
    "text": "Bazinga."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.047,
    "endTime": 275.6,
    "text": "Penny, Leonard. Would you be able to answer some questions I'm having about the events of last night?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.8,
    "endTime": 276.99,
    "text": "Sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.99,
    "endTime": 277.933,
    "text": "Question one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.95,
    "endTime": 280.167,
    "text": "Where are my pants?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.89,
    "endTime": 283.788,
    "text": "You might want to check YouTube."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.05,
    "endTime": 287.1,
    "text": "What do I search?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.2,
    "endTime": 288.92699999999996,
    "text": "It's already loaded. Just hit play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.45,
    "endTime": 295.62,
    "text": "All right, people, let's get down to the math."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.62,
    "endTime": 300.2,
    "text": "It is only three-dimensional thinking that limits our imagination."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.3,
    "endTime": 303.3,
    "text": "Can I take my pants off over my head?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.3,
    "endTime": 304.7,
    "text": "Of course not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.7,
    "endTime": 306.9,
    "text": "And my body's in the way,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.9,
    "endTime": 311.9,
    "text": "but if we had access to higher dimensions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.66,
    "endTime": 323.117,
    "text": "we could move our pants around our bodies through the fourth dimension and our days of dropping trousers would be over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.75,
    "endTime": 329.02,
    "text": "Oh Lord."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.02,
    "endTime": 331.59999999999997,
    "text": "This couldn't be any more humiliating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.7,
    "endTime": 333.127,
    "text": "Oh, give It a minute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.5,
    "endTime": 337.87,
    "text": "Now for the astronomers in the audience, get ready to see the dark side of the moon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.09,
    "endTime": 341.59,
    "text": "And here's Uranus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.427,
    "endTime": 346.0,
    "text": "Hey, Sheldon, you busy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.0,
    "endTime": 347.56,
    "text": "I'm always busy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.56,
    "endTime": 351.18,
    "text": "This mind is capable of advanced multitasking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.18,
    "endTime": 354.53000000000003,
    "text": "Yeah, currently, I'm attempting to solve the Penrose conjecture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.53,
    "endTime": 359.479,
    "text": "I'm composing my Nobel acceptance speech for when I've solved the Penrose conjecture,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.479,
    "endTime": 362.2,
    "text": "and I'm wondering how mermaids have babies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.3,
    "endTime": 366.423,
    "text": "Don't they lay eggs on a rock?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.1,
    "endTime": 370.68,
    "text": "Now I've got room for another thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.68,
    "endTime": 371.651,
    "text": "What do you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.484,
    "endTime": 402.59999999999997,
    "text": "Look, I know our winter thermostat setting is 72 degrees, but I'm a little warm so I'm gonna turn it down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.79,
    "endTime": 406.93100000000004,
    "text": "Good Lord, how you frustrate me, Leonard Hofstadter!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.73,
    "endTime": 412.034,
    "text": "Sing \"Soft Kitty\" to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.847,
    "endTime": 417.7,
    "text": "\"Soft Kitty\" is for when you're sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.7,
    "endTime": 419.37,
    "text": "You're not sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.37,
    "endTime": 421.841,
    "text": "Injured and drugged is a kind of sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.778,
    "endTime": 436.778,
    "text": "♪ Soft kitty, warm kitty, little ball of fur ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 437.807,
    "endTime": 438.73,
    "text": "Wait, wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.73,
    "endTime": 441.877,
    "text": "Let's sing it as a round. I'll start."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.674,
    "endTime": 449.674,
    "text": "♪ Soft kitty, warm kitty, little ball of fur ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.72,
    "endTime": 454.00300000000004,
    "text": "So that's where you come in. I'll start over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.935,
    "endTime": 460.935,
    "text": "♪ Soft kitty, warm kitty, little ball of fur ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.15,
    "endTime": 468.503,
    "text": "I've got all night, Sheldon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.503,
    "endTime": 471.723,
    "text": "♪ Soft kitty, warm kitty ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.723,
    "endTime": 475.035,
    "text": "♪ Little ball of fur ♪ ♪ Soft kitty, warm kitty ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.035,
    "endTime": 478.483,
    "text": "♪ little ball of fur ♪ ♪ Happy kitty, sleepy kitty ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.483,
    "endTime": 481.683,
    "text": "♪ Purr, purr, purr ♪ ♪ Happy kitty, sleepy kitty ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.683,
    "endTime": 486.683,
    "text": "♪ Purr, purr, purr ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.98,
    "endTime": 492.41,
    "text": "Sheldon, there's something else I've been wanting to say,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.41,
    "endTime": 494.36,
    "text": "but before I do, I just..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.37,
    "endTime": 497.95,
    "text": "I want you to know that you don't have to say it back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.95,
    "endTime": 504.637,
    "text": "I know you're not ready and I don't want you to say it just because social convention dictates that- - I love you too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.3,
    "endTime": 511.21000000000004,
    "text": "You said it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.21,
    "endTime": 515.25,
    "text": "There's no denying I have feelings for you that can't be explained in any other way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.9,
    "endTime": 528.6,
    "text": "I briefly considered that I had a brain parasite, but that seems even more farfetched."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.8,
    "endTime": 531.337,
    "text": "The only conclusion was love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.23,
    "endTime": 536.8820000000001,
    "text": "I know what's happening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.54,
    "endTime": 540.457,
    "text": "This is a panic attack."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.457,
    "endTime": 542.95,
    "text": "Soccermama9 says to lie down with your feet elevated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.95,
    "endTime": 543.999,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.999,
    "endTime": 545.89,
    "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.89,
    "endTime": 548.725,
    "text": "Just because I love you doesn't mean girls are allowed in my room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.543,
    "endTime": 551.763,
    "text": "Okay, here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.73,
    "endTime": 558.972,
    "text": "I should note, I'm having some digestive distress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.168,
    "endTime": 564.8100000000001,
    "text": "So if I excuse myself abruptly, don't be alarmed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.161,
    "endTime": 574.76,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.76,
    "endTime": 576.268,
    "text": "A napkin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.05,
    "endTime": 579.423,
    "text": "Turn it over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.17,
    "endTime": 589.793,
    "text": "To Sheldon. Live long and prosper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.54,
    "endTime": 593.15,
    "text": "Leonard Nimoy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.115,
    "endTime": 598.02,
    "text": "Yeah, he came into the restaurant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 598.02,
    "endTime": 600.626,
    "text": "Sorry the napkin's dirty, he wiped his mouth with it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 605.97,
    "endTime": 609.2610000000001,
    "text": "I possess the DNA of Leonard Nimoy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.754,
    "endTime": 619.2,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah, I guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.3,
    "endTime": 621.1999999999999,
    "text": "But look, he signed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.3,
    "endTime": 623.2339999999999,
    "text": "Do you realize what this means?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 626.06,
    "endTime": 630.068,
    "text": "All I need is a healthy ovum and I can grow my own Leonard Nimoy."
  }
]